AddressedMessage, ConsumerIdentifiedMessage, IdentifyConsumersMessage, IdentifyProducersMessage, InitializationCompleteMessage, LearnEventMessage, ProducerConsumerEventReportMessage, ProducerIdentifiedMessage, ProtocolIdentificationReplyMessage, ProtocolIdentificationRequestMessage, SimpleNodeIdentInfoReplyMessage, StreamDataCompleteMessage, StreamDataProceedMessage, StreamDataSendMessage, StreamInitReplyMessage, StreamInitRequestMessage, VerifiedNodeIDNumberMessage, VerifyNodeIDNumberMessage
@Immutable
@ThreadSafe
public abstract class Message
extends Object
implements OpenLcb

Base for all OpenLCB message types

Messages (and therefore all subtypes) are immutable once created.

A Message works with a MessageDecoder object in a double dispatch pattern to do message specific-processing in e.g. a node implementation.

Author:
Bob Jacobsen Copyright 2009, 2010
